title: 95: NFC & AFC East perfect draft pairings
itunes:title: 95: NFC & AFC East perfect draft pairings
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the latest news from the Ole Miss pro day. The guys then give you their perfect draft pairings for the AFC and NFC East.  DJ and Bucky then discuss their Red Star safeties. The guys close with a preview of the final round of the MTS prospect bracket.
